text: Deidre Marie Hulse Henderson (born September 4, 1974) is an American politician. She is the ninth Lieutenant Governor of Utah since January 4, 2021. From 2013 to 2021, she was a member of the Utah State Senate. ==References== Category:1974 births Category:Living people Category:Republican Party (United States) politicians Category:Lieutenant Governors of Utah
title: Deidre Henderson
